---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Projects" description="What VerusAuctor is building.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12">What We're Building</h1>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- THE KICK -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">📖</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">THE KICK</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark font-medium">In Production</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          An 80-chapter literary science fiction novel spanning 35 years. A story about a solar energy system's pilot frequency that intersects an inherited genetic vulnerability to regress every child on Earth — and the impossible question of what humanity is allowed to become in order to survive.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Produced through a 17-agent AI-assisted editorial system with human creative control at every gate. Every editorial decision documented. Every AI contribution attributed. Every human choice logged.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-6 text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary-light dark:text-text-primary-dark">31</strong> of 80 chapters</span>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary-light dark:text-text-primary-dark">217+</strong> canon decisions</span>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary-light dark:text-text-primary-dark">68</strong> narrative elements tracked</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- APH -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">🏗️</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">APH — Agentic Publishing House</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-accent-light dark:text-accent-dark font-medium">Proven in Production</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A 17-agent editorial production system that transforms how novels are written. Strategy, drafting, multi-model editorial analysis, and revision — orchestrated by AI, directed by a human author. The system that proves AI can serve the creative process without replacing the creative vision.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          Proven on THE KICK. Commercial offering in development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ATLAS -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="text-3xl">🌐</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">ATLAS — Agentic Total Local Automation</h2>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark font-medium">Architecture Complete</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          20 specialized AI agents running every dimension of local SEO for businesses. The APH architecture applied to a $75 billion industry. Category audits, review management, content publishing, citation monitoring, competitive intelligence — all autonomous, all compounding.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
          Launching 2026.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
